--------------------------------------------------
GOAL
--------------------------------------------------

Implement a complete quotation lifecycle that begins after an RFQ has been reviewed and approved.

The module must allow:

• Data Updaters to prepare quotations
• Admins to approve quotations
• Customers to view quotations
• Customers to accept or decline quotations
• Automatic preparation for future Order creation

The Quotation module must become the foundation for the future Order module.

--------------------------------------------------
QUOTATION WORKFLOW
--------------------------------------------------

Workflow:

