--------------------------------------------------
BUSINESS RULES
--------------------------------------------------

• Only approved RFQs may generate quotations.

• One RFQ may have multiple quotation revisions.

• Customers may only access quotations belonging to their approved company.

• Every quotation update creates a history record.

• Soft delete only.

• Validate every status transition.

• Never trust IDs from the frontend.

• Prevent IDOR attacks.

• Use optimistic concurrency.

• Support pagination.

• Support filtering.

• Support searching.

• Use DTOs for all requests and responses.

